{"tid":483313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[果然係狗]iOS 11.1.2  輸入「it」竟自動修正作「I.T」","createTime":"2017-11-29T04:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T13:49:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"66e3e4fdbf8d58023e1c26e9da2d6a526a7cb455","tid":483313,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"早日有用戶發現蘋果在 iOS 11.1.1 修復的「自動修正」bug，只是修正了一小部分，iOS 11.1.2 推出了，有用戶發現「自動修正」功能竟然會將「it」錯誤修改成「I.T」，或將「is」錯誤修改成「I.S」，輸入文字從此感到不便。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/11/29/apple-shares-temporary-solution-of-ios-11-it-bug/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2Fapple-shares-temporary-solution-of-ios-11-it-bug%2F&d=wpymXzIE9pr1X%2Be76RV4UJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bce52fba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/11/29/apple-shares-temporary-solution-of-ios-11-it-bug/</a>"},{"pid":"987eebed01c7b7d4ea022472a6af84a52daec256","tid":483313,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f5d537604acc8048321cd00e07ba374bf6e3c0","tid":483313,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"HK no IT"},{"pid":"9e295ad52db7ac6cc82882efc0af4db074880082","tid":483313,"uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"it is a dog(wrong)<br />\n<br />\nGay Cook---&gt;I.T. is a dog(correct)"},{"pid":"e67233803c2413d45344b99bb34a34c7a6722fae","tid":483313,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo